WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.100 --> 00:00:02.466
The day you gave your wife food poisoning

2
00:00:02.466 --> 00:00:03.666
Food scraps found

3
00:00:03.666 --> 00:00:05.966
I'm going to take it for testing. Okay.

4
00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:15.266
Brother, why are you here?

5
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:19.433
Follow me back to the Lu family to pack up and move back to the Bai family

6
00:00:19.900 --> 00:00:21.700
Why don't I go

7
00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:23.166
I don't want to leave the Lu family

8
00:00:23.333 --> 00:00:24.533
Did such an immoral thing

9
00:00:24.533 --> 00:00:26.400
Lost the face of my prodigal family

10
00:00:29.366 --> 00:00:31.333
Garden, what did I do?

11
00:00:31.333 --> 00:00:32.766
You must drive me away

12
00:00:33.366 --> 00:00:34.866
You drugged people

13
00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:37.733
And then give yourself and your mother food poisoning?

14
00:00:37.733 --> 00:00:39.866
I don't have it. I don't have it.

15
00:00:40.266 --> 00:00:42.733
The drug test report and the video of your trip to the pharmacy

16
00:00:42.733 --> 00:00:44.233
Do you need me to send it to you?

17
00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:48.200
Ting Yue, please forgive me

18
00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:49.966
I just love you so much

19
00:00:52.300 --> 00:00:55.366
It was my mother who asked for your wish, so I let you go

20
00:00:55.533 --> 00:00:57.466
Otherwise, what do you think you did?

21
00:00:57.466 --> 00:00:59.566
Just ask the Bai family to pick you up?

22
00:01:00.066 --> 00:01:02.066
Liu Zhiyi, I promise you

23
00:01:02.066 --> 00:01:03.266
He won't show up again

24
00:01:03.266 --> 00:01:04.666
It won't disturb your life

25
00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:05.800
It better be.

26
00:01:07.300 --> 00:01:08.100
Let's go

27
00:01:09.666 --> 00:01:10.866
I'm not leaving

